Peru ' s Banco del Progreso plans $ 50 mln debt issue . Peruvian bank Banco del Progreso plans to issue $ 50 million worth of debt paper on the local market , a company official said Monday . As part of the global bond issue , the bank hopes to issue $ 15 million this year and up to a further $ 15 million in 1998 , Banco del Progreso ' s financial manager Alejandro Velazco said in an interview . Banco del Progreso is the 11th largest creditor of Peru ' s 23 commercial banks . ( ( - - Marco Aquino , Lima newsroom , 511 221 - 2134 ) ) 
